    <item>
      <title>Space Platform Ship Design for All Planets -- Asteroid Defense and Fuel Ratios</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1319/space-age/space-platform-ship-design/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1319/space-age/space-platform-ship-design/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Your space platform is the backbone of interplanetary logistics. A poorly designed ship wastes fuel, gets shredded by asteroids above Vulcanus, or runs out of &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/thruster_fuel.png&#34; alt=&#34;thruster_fuel&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Thruster&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; mid-journey. The ideal ship balances &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/thruster.png&#34; alt=&#34;thruster&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Thruster&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; power, &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/turret.png&#34; alt=&#34;turret&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Turret&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; coverage, and &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/crusher.png&#34; alt=&#34;crusher&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Crusher&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; recycling to become fully self-sustaining.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;pro-tip&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TL;DR:&lt;/strong&gt; The minimum viable ship for all routes uses: 2 thrusters, 4 gun turrets, 2 rocket turrets, 4 &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/crusher.png&#34; alt=&#34;crusher&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Crusher&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;s (1 per asteroid type), and 3 &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/asteroid_collector.png&#34; alt=&#34;asteroid_collector&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Asteroid&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;s on each side. Fuel ratio: 1 chemical plant making &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/thruster_fuel.png&#34; alt=&#34;thruster_fuel&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Thruster&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; per thruster, 1 making &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/thruster_oxidizer.png&#34; alt=&#34;thruster_oxidizer&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Thruster&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; per thruster. Ship width of 5 tiles for the central hub, 3-tile-wide corridors for belt loops.&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;ship-design-principles&#34;&gt;Ship Design Principles&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Every platform needs four systems:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
